回頂端








課程大綱

對豪豬教授來說，教書是一門藝術，每筆揮毫，都引領著學子走向專業的領域；每次雕塑，都提醒著學子應負的社會責任；每刀刻劃，都傳承著對教學、研究、世界的熱情。豪豬教授的專業傳授，豪豬教授的語重心長，豪豬教授的熱情奔放，全都收錄在此!Textbook Mathematical Methods in the Physical Sciences by Mary Boas.OutlineI will cover five subjects in the semester:(1) Ordinary differential equations(2) Tensor analysis(3) Partial differential equations(4) Special functions(5) Complex analysisImportant Dates Week 1 (Sep 13): class begins at 08:00Week 9 (Nov 11): Midterm (Chap 8,10,11,13)Week 17 (Jan 6): Final (Chap 12,13,14) GradesWeekly quizzes (40%)Midterm (30%)Final (30%)



回頂端








課程內容



第1講 Introduction of  Ordinary Differential Equations
第2講 Linear First-Order Equations
第3講 Linear First-Order Equations
第4講 Second-Order Linear Differential Equations with 
第5講 Other Second-Oder Equations
第6講 The Laplace Transform
第7講 Convolution
第8講 Introduction of Tensor Analysis 
第9講  Kronecker Delta and Levi-Civita Symbol 
第10講  More About Applications
第11講 Ch10.9 Vector Operatorsin orthogonal Curvilinear Coordinates
第12講 Definition of the Gamma Function, Recursion Relation
第13講 Introduction
第14講 Introduction
第15講 Laplace's Equation; Steady-State Temperature in a Rectangular Plate
第16講 The Diffusion or Heat Flow Equation; The Schrodinger Equation   
第17講 Legendre's Equation
第18講 Answers
第19講 Leibniz' Rule For Differentiating Products
第20講 Comp;ete Sets of Orthogonal Functions
第21講 Bessel' Equation
第22講 Orthogonality of Bessel Functions
第23講  Steady-State Temperature in a Cylinder
第24講 Poisson's Equation
第25講  Introduction
第26講 Contour Integrals
第27講 Contour Integrals
第28講 The Residue Theorem 
第29講 Methods of Finding Residues
第30講 Evaluation of Definite Integrals By Use of the Residues Theorem
第31講 Evaluation of Definite Integrals By Use of the Residues Theorem









 關鍵字

應用數學(Applied Mathematics)
常微方程(ODE)
偏微方程(PDE)
張量分析(Tensor analysis)
特殊函數(Special functions)
複數分析(Complex analysis)

